Package: ngft
Type: Package
Title: Stockwell or S-Transform (General Fourier-family Transform)
Version: 0.3.6
Date: 2017-05-11
Author: Chris Wood
Maintainer: Chris Wood <cwood@usbr.gov>
Description: R wrappers for the New General Fourier-family Transform
    (NGFT) Library, a complete reimplementation of the Brown et al (2010)
    package cFST-0.1. NGFT is included in this package.
    The GFT includes the Fast Discrete S-Transform (a.k.a. Stockwell Transform) and
    its inverse.
License: GPL (>=3)
Encoding: UTF-8
LazyData: true
NeedsCompilation: yes
KeepSource: true
SystemRequirements: fftw3 (>= 3.1.2)
RoxygenNote: 6.0.1
